name: Surge Inu
description: Surge Inu is a courageous Shiba, reaching new heights wherever he goes! Developed by Shiba Inu fans, it is an ecosystem cryptocurrency that is going to change the memecoin space forever. $SURGE puts the community first, that's why it heavily rewards holders and early investors - 6% of every transaction is redistributed to all holders making your investement $SURGE. Part of the 6% redistribution also transfers to our huge burn wallet, making $SURGE naturally deflationary.
